==Early life== Antonio del Valle Ruiz was born in Mexico.<ref name=Forbes/> He graduated with a degree in accounting from the [[Escuela Bancaria y Comercial]].<ref name=BusinessWeek>{{cite web|title=Antonio Del Valle Ruiz|url=http://investing.businessweek.com/research/stocks/people/person.asp?personId=651358&ticker=MEXCHEM*:MM|website=BusinessWeek|accessdate=17 January 2015}}</ref>
==Career== According to [[Forbes]], del Valle Ruiz has a net worth of $4.2 billion, as of January 2015.<ref name=Forbes/>
