{{Infobox Newspaper | name = Packaging Digest | image = PD Fall Cover.jpg | caption = Packaging Digest Fall 2016 issue | type = [[business]] [[magazine]] | format = Paper and online magazine | foundation = 1963 | ceased publication = | price = | owners = [[UBM plc|UBM]] | executive editor = Lisa McTigue Pierce | founder = | language = [[English language|English]] | political = | circulation = 90,045 | headquarters = [[Oak Brook, Illinois]], USA | ISSN = 0030-9117 | website = [http://www.packagingdigest.com Packaging Digest] }}
'''''Packaging Digest''''' is a trade publication and web site owned by [[UBM plc|UBM]]. It services the [[packaging]] information needs of manufacturing companies who produce consumer packaged goods and products for other markets, such as healthcare.
The executive editor is Lisa McTigue Pierce, with the editorial offices located in [[Oak Brook, Illinois]], USA.
Established in 1963, Packaging Digest is published quarterly, with articles about trends, such as ''Smart-Secure Packaging'', ''Package Design'', and ''Sustainable Packaging'', as well as new technologies and best practices.
As of June 2008, total [[BPA Worldwide|BPA]] audited circulation is 90,045 subscribers.{{citation needed|date=November 2007}}
Former owner [[Reed Business Information]] sold the magazine to [[Canon Communications]] in 2010. [[UBM plc]] purchased [[Canon Communications]] soon afterward.
